{"tid":2336015,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"憂滲透 八成港人反對買內地貴電","createTime":"2020-12-22T09:52:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T01:16:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"201c2ceb1b858cf0cfc25a19aa04441724b0ef3f","tid":2336015,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T09:52:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201222/ECWVZIPZ35GCXN66QMS4AH4QNM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201222%2FECWVZIPZ35GCXN66QMS4AH4QNM%2F&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpHRNzM9MViFDfs2457H6WAQ%3D&h=f2f69cbd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201222%2FECWVZIPZ35GCXN66QMS4AH4QNM%2F&h=4024e992\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201222/ECWVZIPZ35GCXN66QMS4AH4QNM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n憂滲透 八成港人反對買內地貴電<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/whdc0WUpjeRAnVZNLfsRQ7_629g=/1244x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GEA6QW4ZBRCWPFDWKFVQPQWNUU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fwhdc0WUpjeRAnVZNLfsRQ7_629g%3D%2F1244x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGEA6QW4ZBRCWPFDWKFVQPQWNUU.jpg&h=7391fca2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■民眾在家中點起蠟燭照明。<br />\n<br />\n內地停電波及廣東，令。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：冬至斷水電 廣州大贈「㷫」 當局龜縮11小時稱「故障」遭鬧爆<br />\n<br />\n在《管制協議》下，港燈與中電一直佔據着本港主要的電力市場，本港有七成電力均由兩者的本地發電廠透過燒煤和天然氣所供應，其餘三成則由廣東大亞灣核電廠輸入。本港環境局轄下可持續發展委員會去年6月起，曾向公眾諮詢有關從內地輸入更多核能或再生能源，並提出直接連接內地發電廠或廣東電網，以在2050年或之前達到零碳排放的「區域合作」方案。不過據委員會上月公佈的諮詢結果顯示，高達83%市民並不支持有關方案，他們除關注內地核電的成本和安全性外，亦憂慮內地有政治原因。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳洲天然氣平近四成<br />\n<br />\n路透社去年引述消息指，中國要求央企加大在港投資，以獲得香港企業控制權；有分析認為中央或透過控制公用事業，掌控香港命脈。而公用事業戰略價值高，電力更是對民生最具滲透價值的行業之一。此外，本報去年統計發現，港燈過去五年向澳洲和卡塔爾採購液化天然氣，價格平均較中電便宜36.9%，中電主要向國企輸入貴價「西氣東輸二線」天然氣。若中電跟隨港燈從國際採購，近五年可節省120億元。惟中電當時反駁，與港燈的氣源、簽約內容和時間不同，不應直接比較。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者/路透社"},{"pid":"3ff5609f0080c354578fcc448c5d31bc87e21214","tid":2336015,"uid":36383,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T13:23:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cD3Kmo2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcD3Kmo2.gif&h=47118bb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用閃電五連鞭發電"},{"pid":"0d232c576e47132fa17dddce6b22a13a47d0cb79","tid":2336015,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T13:25:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58e47d87c03d53698d3eee46acbb2093f803110","tid":2336015,"uid":86233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T13:30:00.000Z","msg":"其實東江水都係貴過外地買"},{"pid":"9d0d525953d407945e9e5b6361c8127a2bcb9fc1","tid":2336015,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T13:32:38.000Z","msg":"有得你揀咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49bf28887eb7040c48cdb2077b919f34afdf939e","tid":2336015,"uid":71564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T13:44:11.000Z","msg":"住新界同九龍既朋友可以準備停電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04045decc347f05d19780f5f551dfa344e5b3e57","tid":2336015,"uid":34348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49bf28887eb7040c48cdb2077b919f34afdf939e","tid":2336015,"uid":71564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T13:44:11.000Z","msg":"住新界同九龍既朋友可以準備停電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T13:50:24.000Z","msg":"體現港島優越性<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ac56a47c41c0d9d5a7bf1a4874a886c91b10a6","tid":2336015,"uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04045decc347f05d19780f5f551dfa344e5b3e57","tid":2336015,"uid":34348,"li